              li
                p.navbar-text or
              li
                p.navbar-btn
                  a.btn.btn-primary(href='http://app.closeheat.com/users/sign_up') Sign Up Free
    section#home(name='home')
    #headerwrap
      .container
        .row.centered
          .col-lg-12
            h1 Ship Websites Faster
            h3 Don't just talk about it
        .row.centered
          .cta
            a(href='http://app.closeheat.com/users/sign_up') Build a website now
          .col-lg-offset-2.col-lg-8
            img.img-responsive(src='/img/app-bg.png', alt='')
            p.clarity
              | <b>closeheat</b> is a <b>hosting platform</b> and an
              |  <b>intergrated toolkit</b>
              |  for developing websites with languages like <b>Jade</b>,
              |  <b>SCSS</b> and
              |  <b>CoffeeScript</b>.

    #features
      .container
        .row
          h1.centered Blogs, Landing Pages and Front-end Apps Made Easier
          h3.centered Quick start with a website from a template
          br
          br
          .col-sm-12.col-lg-12.text-center
            img.img-responsive.centered(src='img/freedom.png', alt='')
          .col-lg-offset-3.col-lg-6
            .row.clarity
              p.lead.text-center
                | It is easier to change than to create anything from scratch.
                |  Customize the template with <b>Bootstrap</b>,
                |  <b>Angular.js</b>, <b>React.js</b> or drop in anything else
                |  you have in mind.
    #intro
      .container
        .row.centered
          h1 Develop With Ease
          br
          br
          .col-lg-4
            img.feature(src='/img/2.svg', alt='')
            h3 Gulp was Cool but we're Cooler
            p
              | Start writing <b>Jade, SCSS, CoffeeScript and Markdown</b>
              |  - it will just work.
              | Write <code>require('angular')</code> in your code and
              |  <b>we will download it for you</b>.
          .col-lg-4
            img.feature(src='/img/4.svg', alt='')
            h3 One-command Deployment
            p
              | A <b>single command</b> will make <b>your changes
              |  instant</b>.
              | Don't force a designer to learn git just to deploy your app.
          .col-lg-4
            img.feature(src='/img/3.svg', alt='')
            h3 Server with Auto-Refresh
            p
              | <b>Automatic browser refresh</b> every time you
              |  make an edit. Code even faster.
        br
        hr
    #platform
      .container
        .row
          h1.centered Powerful Continuous Deployment Platform
          h2.centered We've got teams on our mind
          br
          .col-lg-7
            #carousel-example-generic.carousel.slide
              // Indicators
              ol.carousel-indicators
                li.active(data-target='#carousel-example-generic', data-slide-to='0')
                li(data-target='#carousel-example-generic', data-slide-to='1')
              // Wrapper for slides
              .carousel-inner
                .item.active
                  img(src='/img/app-screen.png', alt='')
                .item
                  img(src='/img/create-screen.png', alt='')
          .col-lg-5
            p.lead.deploy-clarity
              | <b>Deployment</b> is as easy as <b>pushing your code to GitHub</b>.
              |  Even though it lives on GitHub, your <b>designer can deploy</b>
              |  his changes <b>with a single command</b>. There's <b>no need to
              |  learn Git</b>.
    .container
      .row.centered
        h1 A Platform for Heroes
        br
        br
        .col-lg-4
          img.feature(src='/img/1.svg', alt='')
          h3 Automated Dependencies
          p
            | Just write <code>require('angular')</code> in your code and
            |  <b>we will download it for you</b>.
            |  Updating that package.json is not cool anymore.
        .col-lg-4
          img.feature(src='/img/5.svg', alt='')
          h3 Versioning via GitHub and Instant Rollbacks
          p
            | All of your code lives on <b>GitHub</b>. We'll <b>deploy it everytime
            |  you push a change</b> there. You can <b>preview</b> any of your <b>old
            |  app versions</b> at any time also.
        .col-lg-4
          img.feature(src='/img/6.svg', alt='')
          h3 Convert HTML to Jade
          p
            | You can <b>start developing your old websites on new
            |  technologies</b>.
            |  Transform your files to a new language with a single command.
      br

    .cta
      a(href='http://app.closeheat.com/users/sign_up') Build a website now

    .centered#export
      p
        strong Export anytime!
        |  If you decide to go, you can export your app with
        | a single command: <code>closeheat export</code>

    section#contact(name='contact')
    #footerwrap
      .container
        .col-lg-5
          h3 Address
          p
            | Saltiniu g. 1 - 28,
            br
            | Vilnius,
            br
            | 03218
            br
            | Lithuania
        .col-lg-7
          h3 Drop Us A Line
          br
          form#drop-a-line(role='form')
            .form-group
              input#your-email.form-control(type='email', placeholder='Your email address')
            .form-group
              textarea#your-message.form-control(placeholder='Your message', rows='3')
            br
            button#send-message.btn.btn-large.btn-success SEND IT

          #thanks-note.hidden
            p: b Thank you for everything!
            p
              | We'll contact you as soon as we find this.
              br
              i (usually in a few hours)

          #error-note.hidden
            p: b There were errors sending your message.
            p
              | Feel free to email our CEO directly on
              |  <a href='mailto:domas.bitvinskas@me.com'>domas.bitvinskas@me.com</a>.
              br
              | He'll get back to you a soon as he finds it.
              br
              i (usually in a few hours)
